Minamikawa-san, you really love that drink.

00:21:43.133 --> 00:21:46.367
Yeah, it goes great with everything.

00:21:46.367 --> 00:21:49.100
For me, the happiest moment...

00:21:49.100 --> 00:21:51.467
...is eating grilled offal at Shichimon-ya with a whiskey and coke...

