To be honest, I didn't even invite you.

00:36:28.067 --> 00:36:29.800
It's fine, it's fine.

00:36:30.867 --> 00:36:36.100
Shirasaki, you're going to teach me the secret to Chikuzenni, right?

00:36:36.867 --> 00:36:40.600
I don't know the secret to Ayumi-san's Chikuzenni.

00:36:41.000 --> 00:36:46.000
But I'm going to teach you the secret to enjoying Chikuzenni.

00:37:12.500 --> 00:37:14.200
-Canned tomatoes? -Yep.

00:37:14.200 --> 00:37:15.967
-No way. -Done.

00:37:16.200 --> 00:37:17.933
-You're adding curry roux? -Yes.

00:37:17.933 --> 00:37:19.267
Are you serious?

00:37:31.533 --> 00:37:33.167
I'm thirsty.

00:37:34.767 --> 00:37:35.767
So good.

00:37:36.133 --> 00:37:37.267
Hello.

00:37:37.833 --> 00:37:40.600
"I came to return the key."

00:37:43.833 --> 00:37:45.267
Is that Ayumi?

00:37:54.733 --> 00:37:57.967
I haven't returned your key yet.

00:38:08.633 --> 00:38:09.900
Goodbye.

00:38:13.100 --> 00:38:14.133
Ayumi?

